<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>at the top of the heap • on top of the world</xh5><p> <i>at the top of the heap</i>—(also: at the top of the tree) 1. as high as possible in one’s career or profession: Regardless of who is <u>at the top of the heap</u> in our government we are still the most diverse nation. 2. of the highest rank within a group of items: <u>At the top of the heap</u> are private colleges and universities such as Yale, Williams and Harvard which are world renowned.</p><p> <i>on top of the world—</i>extremely happy: I was <u>on top of the world</u> and it seemed like just the beginning of a long and glorious career.</p> </entry>
